“Akenshi sinari kurira, ariko muri iki gihe sinashoboraga guhagarara.
Umwaka wari utoroshye.
Thomas Nshimiyimana na we yanyishimiye kandi narabyizeye.
Ibyishimo byanjye biranshimisha cyane, ndabyishimira cyane.
Ndashimira Imana kandi nishimira ko yampaye umugisha, " Garcia yampaye ibyishimo.
Yatsinze umukinnyi w'umunyamerika witwa John Rahm ku Cyumweru cya 2 cy'icyumweru.
Umukobwa w'imyaka 23 yagize ati: "Nishimiye ko Woods yansuzuguye mu gihe nari nkiri umwana."
Woods yatakaje imikino ye yose ine mu Bufaransa, ubu afite igikombe cya Ryder Cup cya 13-21-3.
Imibare itangaje y'umwe mu mikino 14 ikomeye yatsindiwe na Jack Nickus.
Uretse Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas na Tony Finau, itsinda rya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika ryari rifite ibibazo mu mpera z’icyumweru cyose.
Umukapitene w’Umunyamerika witwa Jim Furyk yagize ati “ntewe ishema n’abasore barwanye.
Umugoroba w'iburaya wabaye uw'ejo, twari duhanganye n'uyu munsi.
Nta kintu na kimwe twakoze.
Bye bye Thomas.
Ni umukapitene ukomeye.
Bose uko ari 12 bakoze neza.
Tuzamenyana na Komite y'Igikombe cy'Igikombe cy'Abanyamerika.
Ibya cumi n'ebyiri n'ebyiri ni byo binezeza.
Ugomba kwitondera.
Twatsinze."
